1
00:00:04,563 --> 00:00:06,865
♪Schemes within schemes, I prison myself♪

2
00:00:07,095 --> 00:00:10,049
♪Each link swaps bluff and truth♪

3
00:00:10,356 --> 00:00:12,811
♪The world is my Weiqi game board♪

4
00:00:13,118 --> 00:00:18,220
♪Everything's just fleeting♪

5
00:00:19,754 --> 00:00:24,166
♪The play begins♪

6
00:00:26,045 --> 00:00:28,194
♪No return is expected♪

7
00:00:28,539 --> 00:00:33,334
♪The flame is gone, whether we win or lose♪

8
00:00:33,718 --> 00:00:35,713
♪The wind never ceases. I hold the reins♪

9
00:00:35,713 --> 00:00:36,815
[Ashes To Crown]

10
00:00:36,815 --> 00:00:40,815
[Adapted from Xixing's novel, Empress of the State of Chu]

11
00:00:41,572 --> 00:00:43,999
[Episode 22]

12
00:00:45,322 --> 00:00:46,128
Firecrackers

13
00:00:46,281 --> 00:00:47,892
should herald the Chinese New Year.

14
00:00:49,312 --> 00:00:50,770
Yet, while the summer heat lingers,

15
00:00:51,652 --> 00:00:53,033
the air is already thick with the festive spirit.

16
00:00:53,570 --> 00:00:54,836
The blasting has lasted from the Mao hour to the Shen hour.

17
00:00:55,987 --> 00:00:56,907
Everyone's saying

18
00:00:57,022 --> 00:00:58,097
the frontier troops nearly tore apart

19
00:00:58,097 --> 00:00:58,864
the Northern Desert King's tent.

20
00:00:59,516 --> 00:00:59,976
Mr. Xie,

21
00:01:00,782 --> 00:01:01,971
do you still intend to go to the frontier?

22
00:01:02,547 --> 00:01:03,467
The Northern Desert King

23
00:01:03,467 --> 00:01:04,887
is already at the end of his rope.

24
00:01:06,459 --> 00:01:07,879
Why should I get entangled

25
00:01:08,876 --> 00:01:09,682
in this mess?

26
00:01:12,099 --> 00:01:13,019
I'll just send some nobody

27
00:01:13,748 --> 00:01:14,707
to go through the motions.

28
00:01:15,398 --> 00:01:16,855
This was supposed to be our setup.

29
00:01:17,776 --> 00:01:18,582
Had it not been for Xie Yanlai,

30
00:01:18,582 --> 00:01:19,541
Zhong Changrong would be dead.

31
00:01:20,193 --> 00:01:21,612
Once your men in Wangcheng

32
00:01:21,612 --> 00:01:22,341
killed the Northern Desert King

33
00:01:22,610 --> 00:01:24,067
and Liang Qiang moved in to reclaim Wangcheng,

34
00:01:24,451 --> 00:01:25,410
the frontier troops would be ours

35
00:01:25,410 --> 00:01:26,139
for the taking.

36
00:01:27,788 --> 00:01:29,400
That brat's meddling

37
00:01:29,668 --> 00:01:30,435
ruined the entire plan.

38
00:01:31,816 --> 00:01:32,469
What's the rush?

39
00:01:34,118 --> 00:01:35,346
The merit roll still lists

40
00:01:35,499 --> 00:01:36,880
a Xie at the top.

41
00:01:38,530 --> 00:01:39,987
Does it really matter

42
00:01:40,755 --> 00:01:41,330
who leads the troops?

43
00:01:43,095 --> 00:01:44,668
Besides, it's not even certain

44
00:01:46,240 --> 00:01:47,276
he'll live to collect his reward.

45
00:01:48,082 --> 00:01:48,849
Mr. Xie, you mean...?

46
00:01:52,685 --> 00:01:54,066
The moonlight is stunning.

47
00:01:55,064 --> 00:01:56,598
Let's put the celebration banquet aside.

48
00:01:57,941 --> 00:01:59,053
I must first give Mr. Deng

49
00:02:00,319 --> 00:02:01,125
a proper send-off.

50
00:02:10,753 --> 00:02:11,329
Something's on fire.

51
00:02:13,094 --> 00:02:13,822
Not quite.

52
00:02:14,359 --> 00:02:15,549
I've been around enough forest fires

53
00:02:15,971 --> 00:02:16,853
to smell one

54
00:02:16,853 --> 00:02:17,505
before it starts.

55
00:02:36,763 --> 00:02:38,144
The fire spread fast and fierce.

56
00:02:39,294 --> 00:02:40,292
They've drenched the room

57
00:02:40,599 --> 00:02:41,826
in fire oil.

58
00:02:42,402 --> 00:02:43,399
Had I been a moment later,

59
00:02:44,128 --> 00:02:45,010
I would not have made it out.

60
00:02:47,274 --> 00:02:47,811
Deng Yi died

61
00:02:50,458 --> 00:02:51,455
just like that?

62
00:02:53,335 --> 00:02:54,831
I don't usually get along with Mr. Deng.

63
00:02:55,637 --> 00:02:56,634
But I refuse to believe

64
00:02:57,363 --> 00:02:59,089
he would collude with our enemies.

65
00:02:59,626 --> 00:03:00,393
For the moment,

66
00:03:01,161 --> 00:03:01,736
our priority

67
00:03:01,736 --> 00:03:03,309
is to stabilize the court.

68
00:03:04,268 --> 00:03:05,265
Mr. Deng has been confined.

69
00:03:05,956 --> 00:03:06,723
At this moment,

70
00:03:07,912 --> 00:03:08,910
I should step up.

71
00:03:10,137 --> 00:03:11,480
"To stabilize the court"?

72
00:03:13,705 --> 00:03:14,971
"Step up"? How noble.

73
00:03:15,776 --> 00:03:16,390
Xie Yanfang

74
00:03:16,390 --> 00:03:17,541
truly is a master of strategy.

75
00:03:18,385 --> 00:03:19,306
Everything is flawlessly calculated.

76
00:03:19,919 --> 00:03:21,032
The Imperial Guard Office

77
00:03:21,416 --> 00:03:22,758
is still investigating the fire,

78
00:03:23,564 --> 00:03:24,139
and the body

79
00:03:24,446 --> 00:03:25,674
has been sent to the coroner.

80
00:03:32,080 --> 00:03:32,617
Your Highness.

81
00:03:33,921 --> 00:03:34,612
Your Highness!

82
00:03:35,801 --> 00:03:40,213
[Xie Residence]

83
00:03:52,412 --> 00:03:53,179
Your Highness,

84
00:03:53,563 --> 00:03:54,598
I suppose you heard about Mr. Deng...

85
00:03:54,598 --> 00:03:55,634
Did you order his death?

86
00:03:57,552 --> 00:03:58,895
Your Highness, what is this about?

87
00:03:59,470 --> 00:04:00,046
Who else

88
00:04:00,736 --> 00:04:01,618
would dare?

89
00:04:05,263 --> 00:04:06,759
Your Highness, you are mistaken.

90
00:04:08,063 --> 00:04:08,792
There is another

91
00:04:10,902 --> 00:04:12,705
who has the nerve,

92
00:04:14,009 --> 00:04:14,853
the will,

93
00:04:16,196 --> 00:04:18,114
and far more reason besides.

94
00:04:23,293 --> 00:04:24,635
And that person is you,

95
00:04:26,016 --> 00:04:27,436
the Grand Princess.

96
00:04:28,280 --> 00:04:30,006
You and Mr. Deng have long been at odds.

97
00:04:30,658 --> 00:04:31,080
The Grand Mentor's Residence

98
00:04:31,080 --> 00:04:32,423
is filled with the Imperial Guards.

99
00:04:32,768 --> 00:04:34,418
How could suspicion

100
00:04:35,031 --> 00:04:37,832
for his murder ever fall on me?

101
00:04:38,369 --> 00:04:39,635
If I were to kill him,

102
00:04:40,364 --> 00:04:41,591
it would be according to the law,

103
00:04:41,898 --> 00:04:42,742
with clear evidence,

104
00:04:42,780 --> 00:04:44,123
and for all to see.

105
00:04:45,312 --> 00:04:46,310
Is Your Highness suggesting

106
00:04:49,149 --> 00:04:51,489
I am underhanded

107
00:04:53,752 --> 00:04:54,941
and can only operate

108
00:04:54,941 --> 00:04:56,322
in the shadows?

109
00:04:57,320 --> 00:04:58,854
Even if I killed him,

110
00:05:00,695 --> 00:05:02,153
would you really kill me

111
00:05:03,764 --> 00:05:04,953
for revenge?

112
00:05:06,258 --> 00:05:07,485
Are you using this opportunity

113
00:05:08,598 --> 00:05:10,286
to get rid of me as well?

114
00:05:20,106 --> 00:05:21,679
I never thought

115
00:05:22,830 --> 00:05:23,904
that you would be the one to save me.

116
00:05:25,400 --> 00:05:26,436
Mr. Deng, did you really think

117
00:05:27,126 --> 00:05:28,162
a lock could keep me

118
00:05:28,776 --> 00:05:30,004
in that side residence?

119
00:05:31,385 --> 00:05:32,727
I was merely waiting

120
00:05:32,727 --> 00:05:33,725
for the perfect moment

121
00:05:34,377 --> 00:05:35,566
to leave the Capital.

122
00:05:37,599 --> 00:05:38,942
I never imagined that beneath the city

123
00:05:39,747 --> 00:05:41,090
lay such a secret.

124
00:05:41,819 --> 00:05:42,970
In your eyes,

125
00:05:44,197 --> 00:05:44,926
the Capital

126
00:05:45,924 --> 00:05:47,995
is just a board for power struggles.

127
00:05:50,067 --> 00:05:52,138
Father, however, viewed it

128
00:05:52,177 --> 00:05:54,210
as a home to return to.

129
00:05:55,207 --> 00:05:56,205
Over the years,

130
00:05:57,509 --> 00:05:59,734
he remembered everything,

131
00:06:01,537 --> 00:06:03,685
from the halls of noble mansions

132
00:06:03,762 --> 00:06:05,565
to the very number of bluestone slabs

133
00:06:05,603 --> 00:06:07,023
on these streets.

134
00:06:09,286 --> 00:06:10,015
Indeed.

135
00:06:11,396 --> 00:06:12,585
No threshold in the imperial city,

136
00:06:13,314 --> 00:06:14,733
however high, can keep out

137
00:06:15,884 --> 00:06:16,613
those who yearn for home.

138
00:06:17,994 --> 00:06:18,915
I suppose

139
00:06:19,835 --> 00:06:20,641
I am nothing more

140
00:06:20,641 --> 00:06:22,329
than His Lordship's gatekeeper,

141
00:06:23,134 --> 00:06:25,398
entrusted with his most precious holding of all,

142
00:06:26,357 --> 00:06:27,047
this Capital.

143
00:06:27,853 --> 00:06:28,582
It's all fated.

144
00:06:29,963 --> 00:06:30,577
It was written

145
00:06:31,651 --> 00:06:33,914
that I would save you tonight.

146
00:06:37,865 --> 00:06:38,326
Mr. Deng,

147
00:06:38,556 --> 00:06:39,668
your meal is ready.

148
00:06:44,579 --> 00:06:45,768
They have come for you.

149
00:06:46,765 --> 00:06:47,954
Were it not for me,

150
00:06:49,489 --> 00:06:50,832
this is

151
00:06:51,253 --> 00:06:52,788
where your life ends.

152
00:06:54,553 --> 00:06:55,051
Tie Ying,

153
00:06:55,627 --> 00:06:56,049
set the fire.

154
00:06:56,586 --> 00:06:56,969
Let's go.

155
00:07:03,376 --> 00:07:04,718
With this water,

156
00:07:06,215 --> 00:07:06,982
let's toast

157
00:07:08,670 --> 00:07:09,820
to our escape

158
00:07:11,854 --> 00:07:12,851
from the jaws of death.

159
00:07:23,324 --> 00:07:23,938
Was it

160
00:07:25,127 --> 00:07:26,968
Her Highness who wanted to kill you?

161
00:07:27,697 --> 00:07:28,311
It was not her.

162
00:07:30,497 --> 00:07:31,533
It was Xie Yanfang.

163
00:07:33,988 --> 00:07:35,599
To think he could be so vicious.

164
00:07:37,671 --> 00:07:38,592
I favor poison.

165
00:07:39,858 --> 00:07:41,008
Yet he proved even more venomous.

166
00:07:44,921 --> 00:07:46,955
Thank you for saving my life, Your Highness.

167
00:07:47,568 --> 00:07:48,489
What is it you desire, Your Highness?

168
00:07:50,676 --> 00:07:51,558
Speak plainly.

169
00:07:53,016 --> 00:07:53,975
I've bided my time in the depths long enough.

170
00:07:56,238 --> 00:07:57,120
Mr. Deng,

171
00:07:57,120 --> 00:07:58,386
since you're always cautious,

172
00:07:59,499 --> 00:08:00,458
I assume everything that matters

173
00:08:01,225 --> 00:08:02,568
is close at hand.

174
00:08:06,135 --> 00:08:06,903
Please, Mr. Deng,

175
00:08:07,478 --> 00:08:08,437
escort me home.

176
00:08:15,994 --> 00:08:17,145
Can we actually get away?

177
00:08:21,365 --> 00:08:22,324
I have arranged

178
00:08:23,321 --> 00:08:24,280
for someone to die in your place.

179
00:08:27,503 --> 00:08:28,654
That should buy us some time.

180
00:08:40,776 --> 00:08:41,236
Your Highness,

181
00:08:41,658 --> 00:08:42,732
Zhu Yong just reported

182
00:08:43,039 --> 00:08:44,037
that the corpse was not Mr. Deng.

183
00:08:44,957 --> 00:08:45,418
What?

184
00:08:46,722 --> 00:08:47,297
Are you certain?

185
00:08:47,566 --> 00:08:48,563
The coroner has finished the examination.

186
00:08:48,717 --> 00:08:49,369
It is confirmed.

187
00:09:51,860 --> 00:09:52,857
The dew feels chilly.

188
00:10:06,936 --> 00:10:08,202
Your Highness is too precious to fall ill.

189
00:10:10,887 --> 00:10:11,923
Please take care.

190
00:10:32,446 --> 00:10:34,134
It has come to this after all.

191
00:10:34,787 --> 00:10:36,474
With Xie Yanlai's great merit,

192
00:10:37,510 --> 00:10:39,006
the frontier troops under the Xie Family,

193
00:10:39,850 --> 00:10:41,193
and no footing whatsoever

194
00:10:41,999 --> 00:10:43,380
left for you

195
00:10:43,380 --> 00:10:44,147
in Xiao Yu's court,

196
00:10:44,837 --> 00:10:46,525
why suffer under Chu Zhao and Xie Yanfang

197
00:10:47,676 --> 00:10:48,904
when you could come with me to Xiaonan Prefecture?

198
00:10:50,400 --> 00:10:51,320
If I ascend to the throne,

199
00:10:52,625 --> 00:10:54,504
you will still be the Grand Mentor of the State of Chu.

200
00:11:24,350 --> 00:11:25,539
He is indeed not Deng Yi.

201
00:11:26,690 --> 00:11:28,032
Good thing we retrieved the body in time.

202
00:11:28,569 --> 00:11:29,759
If the face had been burned beyond recognition,

203
00:11:30,257 --> 00:11:31,408
it would be impossible to identify.

204
00:11:31,830 --> 00:11:33,288
I fear that should something happen to Mr. Deng,

205
00:11:33,595 --> 00:11:34,362
regardless of whether he lives,

206
00:11:34,400 --> 00:11:35,398
it will be detrimental to Your Highness.

207
00:11:35,897 --> 00:11:36,932
Someone will frame you

208
00:11:37,047 --> 00:11:37,853
for wanting him eliminated.

209
00:11:38,620 --> 00:11:39,503
What does this have to do with Her Highness?

210
00:11:39,771 --> 00:11:40,845
All the officials saw

211
00:11:41,306 --> 00:11:42,418
the Imperial Guard Office

212
00:11:42,610 --> 00:11:44,566
escort him to the imperial city

213
00:11:44,681 --> 00:11:45,487
and lock him in his residence.

214
00:11:45,947 --> 00:11:47,367
Now that the frontier troops have captured the Northern Desert King,

215
00:11:47,789 --> 00:11:48,863
Your Highness's influence is surging.

216
00:11:49,438 --> 00:11:50,474
Eliminating him now

217
00:11:50,742 --> 00:11:52,008
would not stir unrest.

218
00:11:52,469 --> 00:11:53,543
The timing could not be better.

219
00:11:54,118 --> 00:11:55,039
That is nonsense.

220
00:11:55,614 --> 00:11:56,420
Her Highness

221
00:11:56,420 --> 00:11:57,341
has no reason to kill Mr. Deng.

222
00:11:57,494 --> 00:11:58,453
Disagreement in policy

223
00:11:58,683 --> 00:11:59,489
and struggle for power

224
00:11:59,911 --> 00:12:01,062
are reason enough.

225
00:12:03,133 --> 00:12:04,706
If Xiaoman had not been fast enough

226
00:12:05,243 --> 00:12:06,010
to charge into the fire

227
00:12:06,125 --> 00:12:06,931
and drag him out,

228
00:12:07,545 --> 00:12:08,504
we would truly believe

229
00:12:09,156 --> 00:12:09,923
he was

230
00:12:10,077 --> 00:12:11,074
dead.

231
00:12:12,340 --> 00:12:13,337
The first problem

232
00:12:13,337 --> 00:12:14,105
we must resolve

233
00:12:14,603 --> 00:12:15,371
is those issues

234
00:12:15,409 --> 00:12:16,406
you're worried about, Mr. Zhu.

235
00:12:16,752 --> 00:12:17,787
So this body

236
00:12:17,941 --> 00:12:18,938
is a stand-in?

237
00:12:19,821 --> 00:12:20,856
Did he arrange this himself,

238
00:12:20,895 --> 00:12:21,815
or was it someone else's doing?

239
00:12:22,429 --> 00:12:23,580
And what was the purpose?

240
00:12:24,923 --> 00:12:25,882
To fake his death and escape?

241
00:12:26,649 --> 00:12:27,148
Xiao Xun.

242
00:12:28,682 --> 00:12:29,104
Zhu Yong,

243
00:12:29,488 --> 00:12:30,562
go to Xiao Xun's residence immediately

244
00:12:30,600 --> 00:12:31,176
and report back what you find.

245
00:12:31,483 --> 00:12:31,904
Yes.

246
00:12:44,947 --> 00:12:45,715
The entire Grand Mentor's Residence

247
00:12:45,715 --> 00:12:46,712
has been searched,

248
00:12:47,019 --> 00:12:47,940
but there is no trace of Deng Yi.

249
00:12:48,515 --> 00:12:49,397
We kept watch outside,

250
00:12:49,474 --> 00:12:50,663
and not a soul was seen coming or going.

251
00:12:51,277 --> 00:12:51,776
But

252
00:12:52,083 --> 00:12:53,118
there must be something

253
00:12:53,118 --> 00:12:54,001
we missed.

254
00:12:54,730 --> 00:12:55,497
He couldn't just vanish

255
00:12:55,497 --> 00:12:56,264
into thin air.

256
00:12:57,607 --> 00:12:58,221
They knew

257
00:12:58,221 --> 00:12:59,410
you were posted outside.

258
00:12:59,755 --> 00:13:00,561
They wouldn't have moved

259
00:13:01,098 --> 00:13:02,364
without a way out.

260
00:13:04,895 --> 00:13:05,317
By the way,

261
00:13:05,816 --> 00:13:06,852
is Mr. Deng's mother still here?

262
00:13:07,504 --> 00:13:08,578
Everyone in the Grand Mentor's Residence

263
00:13:08,617 --> 00:13:09,691
is under guard.

264
00:13:10,151 --> 00:13:10,918
Mr. Deng's mother

265
00:13:10,918 --> 00:13:12,107
has been placed under separate care.

266
00:13:22,005 --> 00:13:23,424
We searched where Mr. Deng

267
00:13:24,345 --> 00:13:25,112
conducts his affairs too.

268
00:13:26,378 --> 00:13:27,414
The Imperial Seal alone is missing.

269
00:13:31,096 --> 00:13:32,171
That was my oversight.

270
00:13:33,590 --> 00:13:34,396
It is not your fault, Your Highness.

271
00:13:35,585 --> 00:13:36,697
Mr. Deng was under confinement

272
00:13:37,273 --> 00:13:38,078
and yet to be convicted.

273
00:13:39,613 --> 00:13:41,147
No one has the authority to seize

274
00:13:41,608 --> 00:13:42,950
the Imperial Seal gifted by the late Emperor.

275
00:13:43,641 --> 00:13:45,098
Mr. Deng's power and influence

276
00:13:45,789 --> 00:13:46,441
stemmed from the position

277
00:13:46,441 --> 00:13:47,477
granted by the late Emperor

278
00:13:47,554 --> 00:13:48,896
and his possession of the Imperial Seal.

279
00:13:49,510 --> 00:13:50,661
Whether he faked his death

280
00:13:50,699 --> 00:13:51,620
or was taken away,

281
00:13:51,888 --> 00:13:53,116
he would surely take it with him.

282
00:13:56,492 --> 00:13:57,029
Your Highness,

283
00:13:57,796 --> 00:13:58,794
Xiao Xun is gone indeed.

284
00:14:00,750 --> 00:14:01,440
Relay my order.

285
00:14:01,632 --> 00:14:02,745
Lock down all city gates immediately.

286
00:14:04,049 --> 00:14:04,663
Your Highness,

287
00:14:04,855 --> 00:14:05,545
there is a secret passage in the room.

288
00:14:19,432 --> 00:14:20,276
Deng Yi

289
00:14:20,276 --> 00:14:21,350
and Xiao Xun

290
00:14:22,731 --> 00:14:24,266
have finally joined forces.

291
00:14:25,071 --> 00:14:26,107
Once they return

292
00:14:26,107 --> 00:14:27,296
to Xiaonan Prefecture,

293
00:14:28,332 --> 00:14:29,790
they will seize the chance to rebel.

294
00:14:35,697 --> 00:14:37,193
Is the course of fate

295
00:14:38,383 --> 00:14:39,457
truly beyond my reach,

296
00:14:41,413 --> 00:14:43,024
no matter how hard I struggle?

297
00:14:52,461 --> 00:14:52,883
Mr. Xie,

298
00:14:56,413 --> 00:14:57,333
we used poison,

299
00:14:57,333 --> 00:14:58,523
so why did a fire break out?

300
00:14:59,597 --> 00:15:00,517
A minor mishap

301
00:15:00,517 --> 00:15:01,285
from an unexpected twist,

302
00:15:02,589 --> 00:15:03,778
but of no consequence.

303
00:15:04,775 --> 00:15:05,236
Du Qi,

304
00:15:05,926 --> 00:15:06,809
get things ready.

305
00:15:06,962 --> 00:15:07,768
I need to make a long journey.

306
00:15:08,573 --> 00:15:08,995
Where to?

307
00:15:10,069 --> 00:15:11,565
North of the Cang River, to intercept

308
00:15:12,064 --> 00:15:13,330
the Lord of Xiaonan's rebel forces.

309
00:15:16,744 --> 00:15:18,164
Since when did they rebel?

310
00:15:20,734 --> 00:15:21,731
Our grand mentor

311
00:15:22,729 --> 00:15:23,592
is soon to become

312
00:15:23,611 --> 00:15:24,455
theirs.

313
00:15:27,064 --> 00:15:28,061
Only then

314
00:15:29,173 --> 00:15:30,056
will he and Her Highness

315
00:15:30,324 --> 00:15:31,207
be truly locked

316
00:15:31,207 --> 00:15:32,511
in a fight to the death.

317
00:15:34,544 --> 00:15:35,848
This is more intriguing

318
00:15:38,265 --> 00:15:39,339
than my original plan.

319
00:15:44,019 --> 00:15:47,664
- Wish Your Lordship a long life. - Wish Your Lordship a long life.

320
00:15:58,597 --> 00:15:59,057
Your Lordship,

321
00:15:59,479 --> 00:16:00,553
His Majesty's gift has arrived.

322
00:16:01,474 --> 00:16:03,661
I'm glad he thinks of me.

323
00:16:03,661 --> 00:16:04,351
That is enough.

324
00:16:05,540 --> 00:16:06,998
Nothing warms my heart more

325
00:16:07,151 --> 00:16:09,108
than the people of Xiaonan celebrating in the streets

326
00:16:09,415 --> 00:16:10,527
of their own accord.

327
00:16:11,333 --> 00:16:11,716
Indeed.

328
00:16:12,599 --> 00:16:13,941
Distribute these among the people,

329
00:16:14,287 --> 00:16:16,013
so they may share in the joy.

330
00:16:16,550 --> 00:16:16,972
Your Lordship,

331
00:16:17,164 --> 00:16:17,854
you seem to have forgotten

332
00:16:18,353 --> 00:16:19,197
His Highness's gift

333
00:16:19,197 --> 00:16:20,463
arrived

334
00:16:20,540 --> 00:16:21,384
alongside His Majesty's.

335
00:16:22,189 --> 00:16:22,765
Yes.

336
00:16:23,263 --> 00:16:23,877
Bring it forward.

337
00:16:24,453 --> 00:16:25,181
Let me see

338
00:16:25,296 --> 00:16:27,138
what surprise he has for me.

339
00:16:37,687 --> 00:16:38,570
Each character is written

340
00:16:38,570 --> 00:16:40,219
by His Highness himself.

341
00:16:40,449 --> 00:16:40,871
Your Lordship,

342
00:16:41,140 --> 00:16:42,099
this is the Scroll of Longevity

343
00:16:42,099 --> 00:16:43,096
from His Highness.

344
00:16:43,441 --> 00:16:45,475
Such devotion

345
00:16:45,513 --> 00:16:46,856
is truly quite impressive!

346
00:16:49,157 --> 00:16:49,579
Come.

347
00:16:49,771 --> 00:16:50,769
Everyone, take a look.

348
00:16:57,712 --> 00:16:59,016
Xun must have put in a lot of effort.

349
00:16:59,285 --> 00:17:00,359
Writing in such small script

350
00:17:00,896 --> 00:17:02,315
must have strained his eyes.

351
00:17:02,430 --> 00:17:02,968
Indeed.

352
00:17:03,888 --> 00:17:05,730
Each character is written in a different style.

353
00:17:06,267 --> 00:17:07,571
Xun is truly thoughtful.

354
00:17:10,678 --> 00:17:12,558
The scent of the ink is quite unique as well.

355
00:17:12,596 --> 00:17:13,977
His Highness has arrived!

356
00:17:14,898 --> 00:17:15,435
Father!

357
00:17:15,895 --> 00:17:16,394
Father!

358
00:17:16,701 --> 00:17:17,238
Xun,

359
00:17:17,507 --> 00:17:19,003
are you the true surprise?

360
00:17:19,003 --> 00:17:19,463
Father,

361
00:17:19,962 --> 00:17:20,384
quick.

362
00:17:20,652 --> 00:17:21,496
Throw it away! It is poisoned!

363
00:17:21,803 --> 00:17:22,263
Father.

364
00:17:24,335 --> 00:17:25,217
Your Highness, what are you...?

365
00:17:28,248 --> 00:17:28,785
Father.

366
00:17:30,626 --> 00:17:31,087
Father.

367
00:17:31,509 --> 00:17:31,931
Your Lordship.

368
00:17:33,695 --> 00:17:34,156
Your Lordship!

369
00:17:34,501 --> 00:17:35,805
- Father. - Your Lordship.

370
00:17:36,265 --> 00:17:37,186
- Your Lordship. - Your Lordship.

371
00:17:37,762 --> 00:17:39,104
Father.

372
00:17:41,252 --> 00:17:41,674
Father.

373
00:17:42,211 --> 00:17:42,787
Father!

374
00:17:49,807 --> 00:17:50,382
Your Lordship!

375
00:17:50,421 --> 00:17:50,920
Father!

376
00:17:52,339 --> 00:17:52,953
Father!

377
00:17:54,832 --> 00:17:55,408
Your Highness,

378
00:17:55,945 --> 00:17:57,326
what is going on?

379
00:17:57,556 --> 00:17:58,975
Why has His Lordship been poisoned?

380
00:18:05,228 --> 00:18:05,996
The poison lies within the script.

381
00:18:07,530 --> 00:18:08,796
Once inhaled, it pierces the vitals.

382
00:18:12,057 --> 00:18:12,594
Father.

383
00:18:14,589 --> 00:18:15,279
Sir, quick.

384
00:18:15,433 --> 00:18:16,046
Check on His Lordship.

385
00:18:21,379 --> 00:18:22,031
But Your Highness,

386
00:18:22,414 --> 00:18:24,141
you prepared this yourself.

387
00:18:24,409 --> 00:18:25,752
How could it be poisoned?

388
00:18:26,327 --> 00:18:27,133
When the palace said

389
00:18:28,130 --> 00:18:29,089
they would present the gifts to Father

390
00:18:29,089 --> 00:18:30,125
on my behalf,

391
00:18:31,238 --> 00:18:32,197
I gave it little thought.

392
00:18:32,849 --> 00:18:34,230
Once I finished the Scroll of Longevity,

393
00:18:35,074 --> 00:18:36,455
I handed it over to the palace.

394
00:18:37,222 --> 00:18:38,066
But several days ago,

395
00:18:38,718 --> 00:18:39,831
