396
00:18:41,940 --> 00:18:42,938
that my gift

397
00:18:43,743 --> 00:18:45,048
might cost my father his life.

398
00:18:45,815 --> 00:18:47,158
He said the scroll

399
00:18:48,385 --> 00:18:49,306
had been soaked in poison.

400
00:18:50,802 --> 00:18:52,221
I knew Father would pay no mind

401
00:18:52,221 --> 00:18:53,296
