402
00:18:53,986 --> 00:18:54,907
yet would examine

403
00:18:54,907 --> 00:18:56,556
anything from me with great care.

404
00:18:57,323 --> 00:18:58,283
Close enough to inspect it,

405
00:18:59,165 --> 00:19:00,201
he would inhale the poison from the ink,

406
00:19:00,853 --> 00:19:01,236
and...

407
00:19:02,119 --> 00:19:02,426
He

408
00:19:02,771 --> 00:19:03,883
helped me flee the Capital.

409
00:19:04,229 --> 00:19:05,686
I traveled day and night

410
00:19:05,725 --> 00:19:07,029
to stop Father,

411
00:19:07,643 --> 00:19:08,410
but

412
00:19:08,794 --> 00:19:10,750
I was still a step too late.

413
00:19:11,249 --> 00:19:12,515
- Father! - Your Highness.

414
00:19:12,553 --> 00:19:12,975
Your Highness,

415
00:19:13,090 --> 00:19:14,203
you must remain calm.

416
00:19:15,123 --> 00:19:16,926
Is there any way to save His Lordship?

417
00:19:24,062 --> 00:19:24,522
Mr. Deng,

418
00:19:25,021 --> 00:19:26,095
please, save my Father!

419
00:19:26,862 --> 00:19:27,284
Deng Yi?

420
00:19:27,668 --> 00:19:28,435
Why are you here?

421
00:19:29,164 --> 00:19:30,199
Guards, seize him.

422
00:19:30,238 --> 00:19:30,928
You have it all wrong.

423
00:19:32,002 --> 00:19:33,307
It was Mr. Deng who helped me return.

424
00:19:34,496 --> 00:19:34,918
Your Highness,

425
00:19:35,225 --> 00:19:36,107
the person you mentioned earlier

426
00:19:36,337 --> 00:19:36,874
was him?

427
00:19:41,746 --> 00:19:42,322
Mr. Deng.

428
00:19:44,240 --> 00:19:44,623
Your Highness.

429
00:19:44,662 --> 00:19:45,007
Your Highness.

430
00:19:45,199 --> 00:19:45,774
Please

431
00:19:46,004 --> 00:19:47,078
save my father.

432
00:19:47,654 --> 00:19:48,536
I beg of you.

433
00:19:49,419 --> 00:19:49,764
Well...

434
00:19:51,106 --> 00:19:51,528
Mr. Deng,

435
00:19:52,065 --> 00:19:52,718
please,

436
00:19:52,756 --> 00:19:53,677
save His Lordship.

437
00:19:53,945 --> 00:19:54,406
Mr. Deng,

438
00:19:54,636 --> 00:19:55,211
save His Lordship.

439
00:19:55,249 --> 00:19:55,825
Please.

440
00:19:56,170 --> 00:19:56,976
I implore you, Mr. Deng.

441
00:20:00,543 --> 00:20:01,272
Your Highness, please rise.

442
00:20:04,264 --> 00:20:05,607
I do as you wish,

443
00:20:06,489 --> 00:20:07,909
but you must keep your promise.

444
00:20:17,691 --> 00:20:18,228
Mr. Deng.

445
00:20:19,417 --> 00:20:20,568
The poison runs too deep.

446
00:20:22,026 --> 00:20:22,678
He is beyond saving.

447
00:20:24,174 --> 00:20:24,711
Father!

448
00:20:25,248 --> 00:20:26,054
Your Highness.

449
00:20:26,859 --> 00:20:27,281
Father.

450
00:20:28,240 --> 00:20:29,813
Since you told His Highness

451
00:20:29,813 --> 00:20:30,542
about the poison

452
00:20:30,887 --> 00:20:32,345
and helped him escape,

453
00:20:32,614 --> 00:20:33,918
you must know something.

454
00:20:34,302 --> 00:20:34,800
Indeed.

455
00:20:34,839 --> 00:20:35,874
His Lordship has sent His Highness

456
00:20:35,874 --> 00:20:37,102
to the Capital as a hostage,

457
00:20:37,409 --> 00:20:38,521
so who would want

458
00:20:38,636 --> 00:20:39,672
to harm His Lordship?

459
00:20:40,286 --> 00:20:40,746
Mr. Deng,

460
00:20:41,015 --> 00:20:42,358
who exactly is behind this?

461
00:20:44,774 --> 00:20:45,657
The late Emperor.

462
00:20:46,501 --> 00:20:47,038
What?

463
00:20:47,114 --> 00:20:47,613
The late Emperor?

464
00:20:47,767 --> 00:20:48,764
How is that possible?

465
00:20:49,032 --> 00:20:50,222
Mr. Deng, you must be mistaken.

466
00:20:50,567 --> 00:20:52,063
If the late Emperor wanted His Lordship dead,

467
00:20:52,370 --> 00:20:53,636
why wait until now?

468
00:20:54,518 --> 00:20:55,477
I mean

469
00:20:56,513 --> 00:20:57,817
it was the late Emperor who sowed

470
00:20:58,469 --> 00:21:00,349
the seeds of His Lordship's end.

471
00:21:01,538 --> 00:21:02,459
Do you know

472
00:21:02,881 --> 00:21:04,454
who the late Emperor designated

473
00:21:05,259 --> 00:21:06,487
as the Crown Prince

474
00:21:06,679 --> 00:21:08,060
on his deathbed

475
00:21:08,328 --> 00:21:09,786
when the Capital was in peril?

476
00:21:10,477 --> 00:21:11,436
His grandson, wasn't it?

477
00:21:12,165 --> 00:21:12,625
- Yes. - No.

478
00:21:14,581 --> 00:21:15,924
It was the heir to the Lord of Xiaonan,

479
00:21:17,190 --> 00:21:18,034
Xiao Xun.

480
00:21:18,034 --> 00:21:18,379
What?

481
00:21:19,530 --> 00:21:19,990
Is this true?

482
00:21:20,105 --> 00:21:21,256
How can we trust you?

483
00:21:27,394 --> 00:21:29,005
Xiao Xun, heir to the Lord of Xiaonan,

484
00:21:29,504 --> 00:21:30,501
is virtuous, wise,

485
00:21:30,962 --> 00:21:32,611
beneficent to the people

486
00:21:33,072 --> 00:21:34,759
and judicious in governance.

487
00:21:35,565 --> 00:21:36,793
He shall ascend the imperial throne

488
00:21:37,406 --> 00:21:39,094
and bear the weight of the state.

489
00:21:40,897 --> 00:21:42,125
On his deathbed,

490
00:21:42,700 --> 00:21:44,388
the late Emperor named Xiao Xun

491
00:21:44,849 --> 00:21:46,191
as his heir.

492
00:21:48,838 --> 00:21:49,989
The late Emperor

493
00:21:50,411 --> 00:21:52,214
did issue this decree on his deathbed.

494
00:21:52,828 --> 00:21:54,286
I am the witness.

495
00:21:55,782 --> 00:21:57,815
However, Chu Zhao and the Xie Family conspired

496
00:21:58,198 --> 00:21:59,656
to hold the late Emperor hostage

497
00:21:59,656 --> 00:22:00,999
and forced him to issue a new decree.

498
00:22:02,303 --> 00:22:03,224
This imperial edict

499
00:22:04,451 --> 00:22:06,063
never even made it

500
00:22:06,063 --> 00:22:07,290
past the palace gates.

501
00:22:54,283 --> 00:22:54,897
Father,

502
00:22:57,122 --> 00:22:58,196
are you unable to sleep,

503
00:22:59,615 --> 00:23:00,958
or is sleep simply beyond your reach?

504
00:23:05,446 --> 00:23:05,983
Do not fear.

505
00:23:07,786 --> 00:23:08,477
Soon, you will be able

506
00:23:08,477 --> 00:23:09,704
to rest soundly,

507
00:23:11,047 --> 00:23:12,006
never to wake again.

508
00:23:16,725 --> 00:23:18,029
You always loved

509
00:23:18,643 --> 00:23:19,755
to stroke my face like this,

510
00:23:21,750 --> 00:23:23,246
and I always loved

511
00:23:23,591 --> 00:23:24,934
lingering close beside you.

512
00:23:26,622 --> 00:23:27,696
Among all your children,

513
00:23:28,962 --> 00:23:29,883
only

514
00:23:30,880 --> 00:23:31,839
I was blessed

515
00:23:31,839 --> 00:23:32,913
with such affection.

516
00:23:34,064 --> 00:23:35,177
To repay

517
00:23:35,330 --> 00:23:36,136
your indulgence,

518
00:23:36,749 --> 00:23:37,325
now that I've sat

519
00:23:38,821 --> 00:23:40,125
on the throne,

520
00:23:41,621 --> 00:23:43,156
I shall honor you as the late Emperor.

521
00:23:44,192 --> 00:23:45,841
At last, your wish is fulfilled.

522
00:23:48,603 --> 00:23:49,179
Father.

523
00:23:51,058 --> 00:23:51,825
Are you happy?

524
00:23:55,892 --> 00:23:56,774
I am truly happy.

525
00:23:59,344 --> 00:24:00,687
Although I used to say

526
00:24:01,378 --> 00:24:03,334
I wanted to help you fulfill your wishes,

527
00:24:03,948 --> 00:24:05,099
I never knew

528
00:24:05,099 --> 00:24:06,326
if I would feel happy

529
00:24:07,937 --> 00:24:09,203
once they were accomplished.

530
00:24:10,469 --> 00:24:11,735
But now I understand.

531
00:24:13,155 --> 00:24:14,420
So this is what it feels like

532
00:24:15,264 --> 00:24:16,262
to be happy for oneself.

533
00:24:25,430 --> 00:24:26,735
It's finally done.

534
00:24:27,694 --> 00:24:29,535
I should go visit Mr. Deng.

535
00:24:30,647 --> 00:24:31,146
Tie Ying,

536
00:24:31,952 --> 00:24:32,911
bring the Golden Finch Venom

537
00:24:33,294 --> 00:24:33,947
and soak the scroll.

538
00:24:45,608 --> 00:24:46,989
Mr. Deng,

539
00:24:48,255 --> 00:24:49,099
what brings you here?

540
00:24:50,173 --> 00:24:51,056
The decree has reached

541
00:24:51,516 --> 00:24:53,549
Xiaonan Prefecture and the eight commanderies

542
00:24:54,086 --> 00:24:55,237
and twelve cities beyond.

543
00:24:55,506 --> 00:24:57,616
Outside the prefecture, thirty thousand regional troops

544
00:24:57,731 --> 00:24:58,843
have lifted their defenses

545
00:24:59,188 --> 00:25:00,263
and stand ready to be commanded.

546
00:25:00,838 --> 00:25:01,644
I appreciate it, Mr. Deng.

547
00:25:03,638 --> 00:25:06,631
The Prince of State's Residence is stronger than ever

548
00:25:07,359 --> 00:25:09,354
with you on our side.
(Watch on www.kisskh.la to support Admin)

549
00:25:10,390 --> 00:25:11,196
Your Highness is too kind.

550
00:25:12,155 --> 00:25:13,651
It is His Lordship's foresight we should credit.

551
00:25:14,418 --> 00:25:16,259
All those decades of winning loyalty,

552
00:25:17,027 --> 00:25:17,564
and one command

553
00:25:18,216 --> 00:25:19,597
is all it would take.

554
00:25:23,049 --> 00:25:24,123
Yet no command ever came.

555
00:25:25,006 --> 00:25:25,811
Father held it back

556
00:25:26,464 --> 00:25:28,190
for decades.

557
00:25:29,302 --> 00:25:30,453
Without you,

558
00:25:31,374 --> 00:25:32,141
today would have been

559
00:25:32,755 --> 00:25:33,522
no different.

560
00:25:34,788 --> 00:25:35,977
It seems

561
00:25:37,205 --> 00:25:37,972
His Lordship

562
00:25:38,739 --> 00:25:40,197
owes Your Highness thanks.

563
00:25:41,079 --> 00:25:42,575
You willingly threw away

564
00:25:43,036 --> 00:25:44,800
His Lordship's life

565
00:25:45,836 --> 00:25:47,217
for control over the state.

566
00:25:51,015 --> 00:25:52,473
It was my father's wish.

567
00:25:54,928 --> 00:25:56,501
To see it fulfilled,

568
00:25:57,153 --> 00:25:57,997
he cast me aside without hesitation.

569
00:25:58,956 --> 00:26:00,797
Much less would he spare himself.

570
00:26:02,217 --> 00:26:03,176
His death

571
00:26:04,442 --> 00:26:05,247
would be for a worthy cause.

572
00:26:06,475 --> 00:26:07,357
We have secured

573
00:26:08,163 --> 00:26:09,620
the garrison in Xiaonan

574
00:26:09,620 --> 00:26:10,503
and the surrounding local forces.

575
00:26:11,423 --> 00:26:12,613
But progress toward the Capital

576
00:26:12,651 --> 00:26:13,610
is far less smooth.

577
00:26:14,224 --> 00:26:15,643
The Grand Princess has reached out

578
00:26:15,873 --> 00:26:16,564
to all post houses

579
00:26:16,564 --> 00:26:17,945
and prefectures along the route,

580
00:26:18,405 --> 00:26:19,594
and now, most of our decrees

581
00:26:19,594 --> 00:26:20,553
have been intercepted.

582
00:26:25,310 --> 00:26:26,116
Who would have thought

583
00:26:27,228 --> 00:26:28,341
the Grand Princess's decrees

584
00:26:29,070 --> 00:26:30,336
would carry more weight than those

585
00:26:30,412 --> 00:26:31,180
of the Emperor?

586
00:26:33,711 --> 00:26:34,248
Your Majesty,

587
00:26:34,670 --> 00:26:35,936
everything is prepared.

588
00:26:36,512 --> 00:26:37,816
Please proceed to the enthronement ceremony

589
00:26:37,893 --> 00:26:39,197
along with Mr. Deng.

590
00:26:58,071 --> 00:26:59,721
The late Emperor's final decree is here.

591
00:27:00,756 --> 00:27:02,252
In the autumn of the fifteenth year of Tianshu,

592
00:27:02,674 --> 00:27:03,825
I am approaching my end.

593
00:27:04,554 --> 00:27:06,089
Xiao Xun, heir to the Lord of Xiaonan,

594
00:27:06,396 --> 00:27:07,546
is virtuous, wise,

595
00:27:07,968 --> 00:27:09,541
beneficent to the people

596
00:27:09,810 --> 00:27:11,383
and judicious in governance.

597
00:27:11,766 --> 00:27:12,840
He shall ascend the imperial throne

598
00:27:13,262 --> 00:27:14,605
and bear the weight of the state.

599
00:27:15,180 --> 00:27:16,216
Proclaim this to the world

600
00:27:17,022 --> 00:27:18,633
so that all may know.

601
00:27:19,515 --> 00:27:20,589
Kneel.

602
00:27:22,546 --> 00:27:23,812
Kowtow.

603
00:27:25,806 --> 00:27:26,957
Rise.

604
00:27:28,722 --> 00:27:30,026
Kowtow.

605
00:27:33,747 --> 00:27:34,783
You may rise.

606
00:27:37,737 --> 00:27:38,926
Read the proclamation.

607
00:27:40,307 --> 00:27:41,496
On the twenty-seventh day of the eighth month,

608
00:27:41,918 --> 00:27:43,031
in the third year of Xingping,

609
00:27:43,491 --> 00:27:44,527
the Prince of State passed away.

610
00:27:45,179 --> 00:27:46,905
Deng Yi, the Grand Mentor, withdrew to Xiaonan Prefecture,

611
00:27:47,366 --> 00:27:48,708
carrying the late Emperor's final decree.

612
00:27:49,284 --> 00:27:51,509
[The Capital]
No righteous men in court, but traitors within.

613
00:27:51,777 --> 00:27:52,871
During the turmoil of the Yongning year,

614
00:27:53,197 --> 00:27:54,980
the imperial in-law Xie Yanfang

615
00:27:55,268 --> 00:27:57,838
colluded with the frontier troops, took the late Emperor hostage,

616
00:27:58,491 --> 00:27:59,104
usurped the throne

617
00:27:59,565 --> 00:28:00,332
bent the state to his will,

618
00:28:00,677 --> 00:28:01,981
and poisoned the Prince of State.

619
00:28:03,017 --> 00:28:04,015
In the ninth month

620
00:28:04,053 --> 00:28:04,667
of the third year of Xingping,

621
00:28:05,319 --> 00:28:06,853
Xiao Xun, heir to the Prince of State,

622
00:28:07,084 --> 00:28:08,465
acting on the late Emperor's decree,

623
00:28:08,810 --> 00:28:10,076
enthrones Chu Zhao as Empress,

624
00:28:10,651 --> 00:28:12,262
raises arms against the treacherous Xie Yanfang

625
00:28:12,531 --> 00:28:13,605
to restore order

626
00:28:14,065 --> 00:28:15,293
and sets forth on campaign.

627
00:28:21,891 --> 00:28:22,428
Move out.

628
00:28:29,640 --> 00:28:31,098
Deng Yi forged the imperial decree,

629
00:28:31,788 --> 00:28:34,205
claiming the late Emperor intended to pass the throne to Xiao Xun.

630
00:28:35,126 --> 00:28:36,545
He holds the Imperial Seal,

631
00:28:37,121 --> 00:28:38,310
so he can write

632
00:28:38,310 --> 00:28:38,770
whatever he pleases.

633
00:28:39,614 --> 00:28:40,880
The late Emperor was poisoned that night.

634
00:28:41,609 --> 00:28:42,645
Who knows

635
00:28:42,837 --> 00:28:43,565
what the truth really was?

636
00:28:45,368 --> 00:28:46,212
At this point,

637
00:28:46,634 --> 00:28:47,593
what is false becomes true.

638
00:28:48,783 --> 00:28:49,512
Ministers,

639
00:28:49,512 --> 00:28:50,662
do not be disturbed by rumors.

640
00:28:51,468 --> 00:28:53,386
Mr. Xie has blocked the rebel army at the Cang River,

641
00:28:54,000 --> 00:28:55,112
and the Northern Desert King has surrendered.

642
00:28:55,534 --> 00:28:57,145
The frontier will soon be stable.

643
00:28:57,644 --> 00:28:59,255
We have enough energy

644
00:28:59,294 --> 00:29:00,905
and troops to quell the rebellion.

645
00:29:02,056 --> 00:29:03,782
Xiao Xun is merely walking the same doomed path.

646
00:29:04,473 --> 00:29:06,199
Even with Deng Yi, what could a pathetic wretch

647
00:29:07,273 --> 00:29:09,728
like him possibly amount to?

648
00:29:10,572 --> 00:29:12,490
His Majesty will issue the proclamation

649
00:29:12,835 --> 00:29:13,986
and make it known to all.

650
00:29:15,482 --> 00:29:16,096
Court dismissed.

651
00:29:16,863 --> 00:29:19,357
- We bid farewell to Your Majesty - We bid farewell to Your Majesty

652
00:29:19,702 --> 00:29:21,620
- and Your Highness. - and Your Highness.

653
00:29:32,438 --> 00:29:33,896
You were so quick to grasp

654
00:29:34,126 --> 00:29:35,085
"besieging Wei to rescue Zhao."

655
00:29:35,737 --> 00:29:36,850
Why are you struggling so much

656
00:29:36,926 --> 00:29:37,617
with "concealing the dagger behind a smile"?

657
00:29:37,962 --> 00:29:38,768
Zhao,

658
00:29:38,921 --> 00:29:40,034
it's just

659
00:29:40,110 --> 00:29:41,031
so hard.

660
00:29:41,798 --> 00:29:43,410
Can I learn that some other time?

661
00:29:46,670 --> 00:29:47,399
Greetings, Your Majesty,

662
00:29:47,975 --> 00:29:48,780
Your Highness.

663
00:29:50,813 --> 00:29:51,734
Uncle, you're back.

664
00:29:56,222 --> 00:29:57,258
Mr. Xie, you must be exhausted.

665
00:29:58,025 --> 00:29:58,754
I thought

666
00:29:58,754 --> 00:29:59,713
you still had an hour to go.

667
00:30:00,174 --> 00:30:01,593
Fortunately, the meal is prepared.

668
00:30:01,746 --> 00:30:02,667
Please, take a seat and eat.

669
00:30:03,549 --> 00:30:03,971
I appreciate it.

670
00:30:04,547 --> 00:30:05,122
Uncle,

671
00:30:05,544 --> 00:30:06,350
try some and see

672
00:30:06,657 --> 00:30:07,386
if it agrees with you.

673
00:30:16,285 --> 00:30:17,551
There's a new chef in the palace

674
00:30:17,551 --> 00:30:19,009
who specializes in Gaoyang flavors.

675
00:30:19,431 --> 00:30:20,428
Yu finds it quite good.

676
00:30:20,850 --> 00:30:21,656
It tastes very much

677
00:30:21,656 --> 00:30:22,730
like what his mother used to enjoy.

678
00:30:25,147 --> 00:30:26,298
It feels so good to be home.

679
00:30:30,901 --> 00:30:31,592
To see one's kin

680
00:30:32,090 --> 00:30:32,858
is to be home.

681
00:30:40,338 --> 00:30:41,220
The chef brewed this himself

682
00:30:41,566 --> 00:30:43,100
with a traditional method.

683
00:30:43,407 --> 00:30:44,021
Yanfang,

684
00:30:44,366 --> 00:30:45,095
please, have a sip.

685
00:31:00,516 --> 00:31:00,900
Thank you.

686
00:31:01,399 --> 00:31:01,897
Uncle,

687
00:31:02,128 --> 00:31:02,972
try some of this.

688
00:31:03,393 --> 00:31:04,813
This is my favorite.

689
00:31:05,043 --> 00:31:05,350
Very well.

690
00:31:10,030 --> 00:31:10,567
Here, Yu.

691
00:31:14,595 --> 00:31:15,669
I have a chef

692
00:31:15,861 --> 00:31:17,012
who makes exceptional rice cakes.

693
00:31:17,702 --> 00:31:18,470
I shall bring some

694
00:31:18,968 --> 00:31:20,273
for Your Highness to try another day.

695
00:31:21,308 --> 00:31:21,884
Uncle,

696
00:31:21,999 --> 00:31:22,804
can I try some as well?

697
00:31:23,994 --> 00:31:24,761
Of course.

698
00:31:30,438 --> 00:31:30,822
Here.

699
00:31:31,551 --> 00:31:33,085
Uncle, try this.

700
00:31:39,108 --> 00:31:39,914
North of the Cang River,

701
00:31:40,182 --> 00:31:41,218
three commanderies and twenty-eight cities

702
00:31:42,215 --> 00:31:43,481
have all submitted to Xiao Xun.

703
00:31:44,249 --> 00:31:45,208
Together with the Lord of Xiaonan's

704
00:31:45,208 --> 00:31:46,243
illegally raised forces,

705
00:31:47,701 --> 00:31:48,814
the total comes to two hundred and seventy thousand.

706
00:31:49,696 --> 00:31:50,770
I never expected

707
00:31:50,770 --> 00:31:52,074
they could gather

708
00:31:52,420 --> 00:31:53,877
so many troops in just a few months.

709
00:31:54,606 --> 00:31:55,911
Rebellions always begin

710
00:31:56,601 --> 00:31:57,752
with a roar

711
00:31:57,905 --> 00:31:58,903
of momentum.

712
00:31:59,517 --> 00:32:00,207
Deng Yi

713
00:32:00,437 --> 00:32:02,279
stole the Tally and the Imperial Seal.

714
00:32:03,046 --> 00:32:03,928
It is no surprise that many people

715
00:32:04,235 --> 00:32:05,194
have been misled.

716
00:32:07,227 --> 00:32:08,263
In time,

717
00:32:08,800 --> 00:32:10,411
when the court sends forces against them,

718
00:32:11,600 --> 00:32:12,559
people will see the truth.

719
00:32:15,168 --> 00:32:16,242
Just like in the previous life,

720
00:32:16,971 --> 00:32:17,968
Xiao Xun ascends to the throne,

721
00:32:18,851 --> 00:32:20,385
and the one who leads the campaign against him is Xie Yanfang.

722
00:32:27,751 --> 00:32:28,403
Do not worry.

723
00:32:29,669 --> 00:32:30,359
I am here.

724
00:32:32,891 --> 00:32:33,620
I am not worried.

725
00:32:34,694 --> 00:32:35,308
Once Jiu

726
00:32:35,998 --> 00:32:37,456
escorted the Northern Desert King across the frontier,

727
00:32:38,108 --> 00:32:39,182
he could lead the troops

728
00:32:39,182 --> 00:32:40,257
to provide support

729
00:32:40,717 --> 00:32:41,484
and form a pincer movement

730
00:32:41,484 --> 00:32:42,520
with the court's forces.

731
00:32:42,942 --> 00:32:44,438
The Lord of Xiaonan's rebels

732
00:32:44,706 --> 00:32:45,397
will be crushed.

733
00:32:48,619 --> 00:32:49,387
Do you miss him?

734
00:32:53,223 --> 00:32:53,798
What?

735
00:33:25,331 --> 00:33:26,099
The time has come.

736
00:33:27,058 --> 00:33:27,556
Let's go.

737
00:33:28,592 --> 00:33:30,127
Chu Ling must have wished

738
00:33:30,740 --> 00:33:32,505
to storm my tent

739
00:33:33,464 --> 00:33:34,845
just as you did.

740
00:33:35,651 --> 00:33:36,955
It is precisely because General Chu

741
00:33:36,955 --> 00:33:38,221
kept you locked in battle for decades

742
00:33:39,333 --> 00:33:40,523
that I now have the chance

743
00:33:40,638 --> 00:33:41,635
to take you down.

744
00:33:42,364 --> 00:33:43,361
You are very valorous.

745
00:33:45,088 --> 00:33:46,162
Your father

746
00:33:47,236 --> 00:33:48,617
must have been proud of you.

747
00:33:55,599 --> 00:33:57,287
My son is much stronger than you.

748
00:33:58,629 --> 00:34:01,852
He knew his father loved him until the very end.

749
00:34:09,831 --> 00:34:10,905
I have one last question for you.

750
00:34:13,322 --> 00:34:14,281
What really happened

751
00:34:14,971 --> 00:34:16,889
with that fire in the Wei Village

752
00:34:17,580 --> 00:34:19,114
five years ago?

753
00:34:24,408 --> 00:34:25,828
Back then, Chu Yan had Alan Ruoying

754
00:34:26,077 --> 00:34:29,127
survive as the leader of a band of bandits,

755
00:34:29,184 --> 00:34:30,067
Mu Mianhong,

756
00:34:30,489 --> 00:34:32,368
and hide in the Cangmu Forest.

757
00:34:33,231 --> 00:34:34,401
So, we decided

758
00:34:34,401 --> 00:34:36,109
to make a deal with the Lord of Xiaonan.

759
00:34:36,320 --> 00:34:38,007
We set a fire at the Wei Village

760
00:34:38,007 --> 00:34:39,772
at the foot of the Cangmu Forest

761
00:34:40,156 --> 00:34:41,230
and left clues

762
00:34:41,230 --> 00:34:42,918
to frame the Cangmu Stronghold.

763
00:34:43,263 --> 00:34:44,778
Once the court of the State of Chu

764
00:34:44,778 --> 00:34:46,102
followed our lead

765
00:34:46,102 --> 00:34:47,483
to investigate the stronghold,

766
00:34:48,365 --> 00:34:50,091
they would discover

767
00:34:50,091 --> 00:34:51,396
Mu Mianhong's true identity,

768
00:34:52,125 --> 00:34:53,036
which would serve

769
00:34:53,045 --> 00:34:54,887
as ironclad proof of Chu Ling's treason.

770
00:34:55,539 --> 00:34:57,879
If Yunzhong Prefecture lost Chu Ling,

771
00:34:58,377 --> 00:35:00,871
seizing the frontier would be a simple task.

772
00:35:01,638 --> 00:35:03,173
I do not know

773
00:35:03,403 --> 00:35:05,513
why the clues pointing to the Cangmu Stronghold were erased,

774
00:35:05,935 --> 00:35:07,814
and why you appeared

775
00:35:07,814 --> 00:35:09,157
in that fire

776
00:35:09,579 --> 00:35:10,874
and ended up

777
00:35:10,883 --> 00:35:13,070
taking the blame for us.

778
00:35:13,549 --> 00:35:14,547
Later,

779
00:35:16,388 --> 00:35:18,805
I heard that the young man from the Xie Family

780
00:35:18,805 --> 00:35:20,992
framed for burning the village had gone to the frontier

781
00:35:21,663 --> 00:35:23,140
and become the most capable vanguard

782
00:35:23,140 --> 00:35:24,367
by Chu Ling's side.

783
00:35:25,288 --> 00:35:27,283
As they say in the Central Plains,

784
00:35:27,858 --> 00:35:29,431
the world never unfolds as planned.

785
00:35:30,582 --> 00:35:31,656
I never imagined

786
00:35:32,769 --> 00:35:34,015
we would meet again

787
00:35:34,015 --> 00:35:35,627
on the battlefield like this.

788
00:35:36,912 --> 00:35:37,832
Now

789
00:35:38,791 --> 00:35:39,904
you have settled

790
00:35:39,904 --> 00:35:41,247
the debt of that injustice.

791
00:35:44,737 --> 00:35:45,965
General, we are under attack.

792
00:35:46,080 --> 00:35:46,924
We have been surrounded.

793
00:35:49,456 --> 00:35:50,223
Is it someone looking for you?

794
00:35:51,412 --> 00:35:52,602
Who wants you dead?

795
00:35:54,251 --> 00:35:55,671
It could be anyone.

796
00:35:56,016 --> 00:35:57,550
To claim the throne,

797
00:35:57,665 --> 00:35:59,277
one must first remove the predecessor.

798
00:36:00,696 --> 00:36:01,770
I want to see

799
00:36:03,304 --> 00:36:04,916
who can actually take my life.

800
00:36:04,916 --> 00:36:06,258
You can butcher each other for all I care,

801
00:36:07,064 --> 00:36:07,601
but

802
00:36:08,560 --> 00:36:10,210
you must not die within the State of Chu.

803
00:36:10,708 --> 00:36:11,245
Follow me.

804
00:36:12,089 --> 00:36:12,511
Hurry.

805
00:36:20,989 --> 00:36:21,411
Go!

806
00:36:53,827 --> 00:36:54,249
Mr. Xie,

807
00:36:55,783 --> 00:36:56,646
I heard that Her Highness

808
00:36:56,646 --> 00:36:57,471
is personally leading another campaign.

809
00:36:58,085 --> 00:36:59,197
Has she developed a taste for war,

810
00:37:00,156 --> 00:37:00,885
or

811
00:37:01,499 --> 00:37:02,957
is she acting out of spite because Xiao Xun declared

812
00:37:03,571 --> 00:37:04,338
he would take her as his Empress?

813
00:37:05,105 --> 00:37:06,102
Regardless of the reason,

814
00:37:07,483 --> 00:37:08,634
if she wants to do it, she should go.

815
00:37:09,363 --> 00:37:10,706
We need only pave the road for her,

816
00:37:11,972 --> 00:37:13,161
just like the dead-end road

817
00:37:14,005 --> 00:37:15,348
we paved for Yanlai.

818
00:37:17,227 --> 00:37:18,263
I received a secret report.

819
00:37:21,390 --> 00:37:22,540
Yanlai is dead.

820
00:37:23,288 --> 00:37:24,708
He died believing

821
00:37:25,533 --> 00:37:27,029
that the ones who attacked him and the Northern Desert King

822
00:37:27,930 --> 00:37:29,081
were Xiao Xun's men.

823
00:37:29,580 --> 00:37:30,731
You are truly far-sighted.

824
00:37:33,876 --> 00:37:35,142
Deng Yi dying at her hands

825
00:37:36,331 --> 00:37:37,866
is better than him dying at mine.

826
00:37:38,671 --> 00:37:39,861
They started with an alliance

827
00:37:40,244 --> 00:37:41,433
and ended up shattered by infighting.

828
00:37:42,853 --> 00:37:44,694
Once she learns of Yanlai's death,

829
00:37:46,305 --> 00:37:47,437
there will be no reconciliation

830
00:37:47,456 --> 00:37:48,377
between her and Xiao Xun.

831
00:37:52,136 --> 00:37:52,597
Well,

832
00:37:54,400 --> 00:37:55,090
are the night refreshments ready?

833
00:37:56,241 --> 00:37:56,893
Yes.

834
00:37:57,162 --> 00:37:58,236
Have them packed

835
00:37:59,157 --> 00:38:00,192
and delivered to Her Highness.

836
00:38:00,768 --> 00:38:02,264
You are far too good to her, Mr. Xie,

837
00:38:02,878 --> 00:38:03,683
yet gratitude

838
00:38:03,683 --> 00:38:04,565
is not in her nature.

839
00:38:05,294 --> 00:38:06,445
I don't know what you are aiming for.

840
00:38:12,391 --> 00:38:13,734
The better I treat her now,

841
00:38:15,153 --> 00:38:15,882
the greater

842
00:38:15,882 --> 00:38:17,417
her agony will be.

843
00:38:19,258 --> 00:38:20,294
Once she kills Xiao Xun

844
00:38:21,406 --> 00:38:23,094
and returns covered in wounds,

845
00:38:24,782 --> 00:38:26,508
I must ensure she has a place to return to.

846
00:38:33,682 --> 00:38:34,794
That scoundrel Xiao Xun

847
00:38:35,140 --> 00:38:35,984
actually dared to declare

848
00:38:35,984 --> 00:38:36,866
that he would take Your Highness as his empress.

849
00:38:39,168 --> 00:38:40,683
All he wants is for me to become

850
00:38:40,683 --> 00:38:41,431
what he is,

851
00:38:42,275 --> 00:38:43,694
a rebel who seized the throne

852
00:38:44,385 --> 00:38:45,612
and deserves to be struck down

853
00:38:45,612 --> 00:38:46,341
by all.

854
00:38:46,380 --> 00:38:46,763
Your Highness,

855
00:38:47,109 --> 00:38:48,106
you should march out with the troops now

856
00:38:48,413 --> 00:38:49,372
and claim his head

857
00:38:49,640 --> 00:38:50,561
before the eyes of the world.

858
00:39:07,018 --> 00:39:07,670
Your Highness,

859
00:39:08,284 --> 00:39:09,397
are you feeling unwell?

860
00:39:10,087 --> 00:39:10,816
I don't know what is wrong.

861
00:39:12,389 --> 00:39:13,309
I feel terribly anxious.

862
00:39:26,352 --> 00:39:27,427
My chances of winning are higher

863
00:39:28,347 --> 00:39:29,383
in this battle against Xiao Xun.

864
00:39:29,920 --> 00:39:30,879
Even if it is difficult to defy fate,

865
00:39:31,224 --> 00:39:32,759
at worst, we will fight to the death.

866
00:39:34,255 --> 00:39:35,252
Yet why

867
00:39:36,173 --> 00:39:37,170
does my heart feel so unsettled?

868
00:39:39,971 --> 00:39:40,393
Your Highness,

869
00:39:40,815 --> 00:39:41,467
urgent report from the frontier.

870
00:39:42,042 --> 00:39:42,656
What has happened at the frontier?

871
00:39:43,769 --> 00:39:44,574
It is General Fu Jiu.

872
00:39:46,607 --> 00:39:47,221
What about Jiu?

873
00:39:47,912 --> 00:39:48,832
General Fu Jiu and the Northern Desert King

874
00:39:49,446 --> 00:39:50,405
were ambushed by an unknown army.

875
00:39:50,981 --> 00:39:51,748
Whether they survived is unclear.

876
00:40:14,074 --> 00:40:14,726
Are you going to the frontier?

877
00:40:15,494 --> 00:40:15,839
Yes.

878
00:40:16,606 --> 00:40:17,335
Must you go?

879
00:40:18,371 --> 00:40:19,138
Yes.

880
00:40:19,905 --> 00:40:20,979
He is dead.

881
00:40:31,030 --> 00:40:31,836
No body means

882
00:40:33,063 --> 00:40:34,521
there is still a chance.

883
00:40:35,672 --> 00:40:36,669
I believe General Zhong

884
00:40:37,782 --> 00:40:38,817
has been looking for him.

885
00:40:42,040 --> 00:40:43,037
If you are worried,

886
00:40:45,723 --> 00:40:46,873
I will send more men.

887
00:40:48,485 --> 00:40:49,329
If he is alive,

888
00:40:50,594 --> 00:40:51,630
I will retrieve him myself.

889
00:40:52,896 --> 00:40:53,472
If he is gone,

890
00:40:55,236 --> 00:40:57,001
I will do everything in my power to uncover the truth.

891
00:40:59,034 --> 00:41:00,147
You are the Grand Princess.

892
00:41:01,221 --> 00:41:02,793
Xiao Xun has risen in revolt,

893
00:41:03,829 --> 00:41:04,290
and

894
00:41:04,290 --> 00:41:05,095
you would leave the court

895
00:41:05,095 --> 00:41:05,901
over something so absurd?

896
00:41:07,013 --> 00:41:08,164
If something happens,

897
00:41:09,468 --> 00:41:10,926
you will regret it forever.

898
00:41:11,770 --> 00:41:13,113
Do you think I am doing this

899
00:41:13,113 --> 00:41:14,225
only for one Xie Yanlai?

900
00:41:15,568 --> 00:41:16,642
As the Grand Princess,

901
00:41:17,870 --> 00:41:19,212
if I remain indifferent to the unjust death

902
00:41:20,900 --> 00:41:22,166
of a loyal general,

903
00:41:23,931 --> 00:41:25,312
who else will be willing to give their life for the state?

904
00:41:49,173 --> 00:41:49,786
Xie Yanfang,

905
00:41:51,283 --> 00:41:52,165
you dare try to kill me?

906
00:41:52,855 --> 00:41:54,083
By leaving the court without sanction, Your Highness

907
00:41:54,083 --> 00:41:54,965
is putting the very foundation of the state at risk.

908
00:41:55,502 --> 00:41:56,423
Since I am aware of this,

909
00:41:56,423 --> 00:41:57,420
I cannot ignore it.

910
00:41:58,648 --> 00:41:59,684
If you come back with me,

911
00:42:00,336 --> 00:42:02,062
I will pretend nothing happened.

912
00:42:39,311 --> 00:42:43,723
♪Broken walls and withered branches, trapped in the mire♪

913
00:42:43,991 --> 00:42:46,370
♪Yet still striving to reach for the sky♪

914
00:42:46,408 --> 00:42:50,283
♪My pride is torn down and my body is sacrificed♪

915
00:42:52,431 --> 00:42:54,464
♪The spark smolders in the crack♪

916
00:42:54,541 --> 00:42:56,421
♪And roars in the blaze♪

917
00:42:56,497 --> 00:42:59,605
♪Burning the cold night until daybreak♪

918
00:42:59,758 --> 00:43:01,906
♪Fate imprisons me♪

919
00:43:02,060 --> 00:43:06,663
♪But I won't beg the abyss for mercy♪

920
00:43:06,663 --> 00:43:10,691
♪Even if hope is faint, I remain proud♪

921
00:43:10,691 --> 00:43:14,796
♪A mayfly will cross the ocean, however long it takes♪

922
00:43:14,796 --> 00:43:20,013
♪However it ends up, I'll go my own way♪

923
00:43:20,013 --> 00:43:21,893
♪With no fear of the distance♪

924
00:43:21,893 --> 00:43:25,460
♪Born from decay, fireflies still burn♪

925
00:43:25,460 --> 00:43:29,718
♪With sword in hand, I'll pierce the dawn♪

926
00:43:29,718 --> 00:43:34,859
♪Let these scars all over me become♪

927
00:43:34,859 --> 00:43:38,311
♪My new pride♪

928
00:43:52,505 --> 00:43:55,267
♪Peril is everywhere in the palace♪

929
00:43:55,267 --> 00:43:57,684
♪Yet I smile to nobody but you♪

930
00:43:57,684 --> 00:43:59,947
♪Amidst the chaos♪

931
00:43:59,947 --> 00:44:04,052
♪I'll always be with you♪

932
00:44:05,433 --> 00:44:07,466
♪The spark smolders in the crack♪

933
00:44:07,543 --> 00:44:09,423
♪And roars in the blaze♪

934
